  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nCast\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nThe following `cast` functions uses `https://sig.eth.samczsun.com` by default to lookup signature calls.\r\n* `4byte-event` \r\n* `4byte-decode` \r\n* `4byte`\r\n\r\nI'll like to be able to define self-hosted endpoints via an option like `--sig-url=https://4byte.mysite.com`\r\n\r\nOthers may want to do it to avoid exposing API calls to the service provider or exposing function selectors to the public. This will also reduce reliance on the site being online.\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
