    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Can you explain a bit more ? I don't think there is a standard API for this, `https://www.4byte.directory` uses a totally different one than `https://sig.eth.samczsun.com`, which is currently implemented.\r\n\r\nImplementing the ability to query another endpoint with the same API as the latter is not a big change.\r\nBut I'm not sure it's good to start implementing multiple APIs for this, cast used to support the 4bytes API but it has been replaced, see https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/1672\r\n",
